  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为教育场景设计一个语音翻译系统的状态机。核心流程是：学生从内容CDN进入系统后，先处于Idle状态，按下录音按钮后进入Recording，检测到语音结束就转到Processing做ASR和翻译，最后根据配置决定是Playing语音还是直接显示结果。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Idle",
        "Recording",
        "Processing",
        "Playing"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，Idle是初始状态。我想确认一下：Recording到Processing的触发条件是\"检测到语音结束\"，那如果用户中途取消呢？是否需要一条回到Idle的路径？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Recording",
        "Idle",
        "Processing"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，需要加上。Recording到Idle的触发条件是\"用户取消\"，同时要清理资源。另外Processing也有失败的情况，得有个Error状态，处理失败时跳过去。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Recording",
        "Idle",
        "Processing",
        "Error"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经把Recording→Idle和Processing→Error加上去了。Error之后怎么恢复？还有，严重错误时系统是不是要直接终止？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Error",
        "Idle",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Error可以回到Idle，条件是用户确认清除错误。但如果是严重错误，比如数据库连接断了，就直接终止到Education_StudentDB。另外Processing完成后，如果TTS启用就Playing，禁用就直接回Idle显示文字结果。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Error",
        "Idle",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Processing",
        "Playing"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "清楚了。Playing结束后的归宿是Idle，对吧？还有用户中断播放的情况。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Playing",
        "Idle"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，Playing到Idle有两条路径：播放完成重置状态，或者用户中断停止播放。最后给Recording和Processing加个注释，说明VAD监控、ASR转录这些内部细节。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Playing",
        "Idle",
        "Recording",
        "Processing"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "都加上了。Recording旁边注明了VAD持续监控、Partial即时更新、音频串流至ASR；Processing旁边是ASR转录、翻译引擎处理、储存对话记录。整个状态机应该完整了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Recording",
        "Processing"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
